This fixer-upper boasts a spacious full unfinished walk-out basement, already stubbed for a bath, offering ample opportunity for customization and expansion. SOLD AS IS, this property presents a canvas for your creative vision to flourish. While the deck requires replacement, envision the possibilities for outdoor entertainment and relaxation. Seize the chance to transform this house into your dream home!
